bd6e5a3d1e4df026bec76fdccc27772d4cf","tid":233693,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"近窗橫放張六呎床，床尾剩一呎做個一呎厚既櫃，闊就齊張床3呎，當係電視櫃。呢個櫃既下半部會俾你張床擋左，所以做個側門，入面可以放埋雜物。"},{"pid":"20169e29a5936beebe2eaba885e695337c7cb345","tid":233693,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得太多野逼埋一齊好無空間感,好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n係香港就要接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fb61d228e75e3f5c00dc9ee1457f316ae5b904","tid":233693,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近窗橫放張六呎床，床尾剩一呎做個一呎厚既櫃，闊就齊張床3呎，當係電視櫃。呢個櫃既下半部會俾你張床擋左，所以做個側門，入面可以放埋雜物。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg&h=aae8612b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc6160958d47e936878525786c9b7378fa9cf0fd","tid":233693,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近窗橫放張六呎床，床尾剩一呎做個一呎厚既櫃，闊就齊張床3呎，當係電視櫃。呢個櫃既下半部會俾你張床擋左，所以做個側門，入面可以放埋雜物。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg&h=aae8612b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32WqUYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32WqUYO.jpg&h=e312d903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5736097697ab4d7ab7691e41ddc3461db0e5b13","tid":233693,"uid":70763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2HvUM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2HvUM6.jpg&h=b2af6bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36AQZC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36AQZC5.jpg&h=b3676a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umF6RM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumF6RM4.jpg&h=fe97af3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前住雜物房嗰陣都係類似咁擺<br />\n不過係碌架床下面係衣櫃<br />\n再連住張枱喺有窗口幅牆度<br />\n咁樣住落<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似</span>冇咁逼"},{"pid":"fd389d31aa678108ff9b91a466127f914d94bc6c","tid":233693,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近窗橫放張六呎床，床尾剩一呎做個一呎厚既櫃，闊就齊張床3呎，當係電視櫃。呢個櫃既下半部會俾你張床擋左，所以做個側門，入面可以放埋雜物。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F101043_e42d0cbcb0b6f8c9d9892ebebfbc2ee6.jpg&h=aae8612b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32WqUYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32WqUYO.jpg&h=e312d903&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以買d下面有幾格櫃桶放衫既床，多衫買六格，少就三格"},{"pid":"02f35bc5b519ef66b2edc8aad9a6990277595283","tid":233693,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"我間房再細樓主少少，應該6呎x7呎。<br />\n<br />\n右邊: 上面衣櫃下面床<br />\n左邊: 書枱+層架<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係上面床下面櫃+書枱，間房個感覺會好壓迫，改完之後正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994c8c9a457a0c226d710dd79bd6087d6ebc9ef8","tid":233693,"uid":47354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2HvUM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2HvUM6.jpg&h=b2af6bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36AQZC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36AQZC5.jpg&h=b3676a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umF6RM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumF6RM4.jpg&h=fe97af3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我張床直頭係呢張 ikea買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係有個櫃 但唔係側擺"},{"pid":"54f17fd3b6245f4bd00f2f28f6a84974261df8f4","tid":233693,"uid":78718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/073902_baa936b659cd0a3dbfebd27fe886e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F073902_baa936b659cd0a3dbfebd27fe886e9e5.jpg&h=7e83e593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我間房 要用電腦時 床變番梳化"},{"pid":"249e083da916d4a3778e163d28d311541d429b56","tid":233693,"uid":44780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間房再細樓主少少，應該6呎x7呎。<br />\n<br />\n右邊: 上面衣櫃下面床<br />\n左邊: 書枱+層架<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係上面床下面櫃+書枱，間房個感覺會好壓迫，改完之後正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetail pls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d8016a8cd2d9214b9d0a54de30e6aa75d31e9d","tid":233693,"uid":52239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"換趟門"},{"pid":"6168dc2d47a4c5441e98d3a19fc0022f138cfe70","tid":233693,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得太多野逼埋一齊好無空間感,好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n係香港就要接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係既, 其實係個設計問題,同埋唔可以要求太多櫃擺野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簡簡單單一張床,一個櫃/掛櫃 咪算"},{"pid":"ffb40dd6ea8b3572656dadf8fde904b8aabfd40a","tid":233693,"uid":18367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得唔好做地台</blockquote><br />\n點解既"},{"pid":"c6f40c5d6720ad1667d02c02674ac480774e9b3d","tid":233693,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/073902_baa936b659cd0a3dbfebd27fe886e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F073902_baa936b659cd0a3dbfebd27fe886e9e5.jpg&h=7e83e593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我間房 要用電腦時 床變番梳化</blockquote><br />\n咁個窗未會差唔多遮左 向右90度咁擺唔係會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2883f5f058fab36bf91c712a7bb7f33a5716aff2","tid":233693,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我間房再細樓主少少，應該6呎x7呎。<br />\n<br />\n右邊: 上面衣櫃下面床<br />\n左邊: 書枱+層架<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係上面床下面櫃+書枱，間房個感覺會好壓迫，改完之後正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetail pls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y07djh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY07djh6.jpg&h=39fabae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面衣櫃下面床係講緊呢款，床底仲有三個櫃，應該夠晒擺衫同雜物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02FW7o5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02FW7o5.jpg&h=d34ef892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平面圖係咁上下，唔係好識畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其實想影自己間房比你睇，不過唔想自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲床同書枱係一set咁訂造，我160cm，所以張床造短左，床尾用黎放喼同埋鞋盒。自己再喺房痴啲牆貼同poster，間房就靚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f515671bab628042183810b02323aa408aa3233a","tid":233693,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我間房再細樓主少少，應該6呎x7呎。<br />\n<br />\n右邊: 上面衣櫃下面床<br />\n左邊: 書枱+層架<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係上面床下面櫃+書枱，間房個感覺會好壓迫，改完之後正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetail pls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y07djh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY07djh6.jpg&h=39fabae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面衣櫃下面床係講緊呢款，床底仲有三個櫃，應該夠晒擺衫同雜物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02FW7o5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02FW7o5.jpg&h=d34ef892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平面圖係咁上下，唔係好識畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其實想影自己間房比你睇，不過唔想自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲床同書枱係一set咁訂造，我160cm，所以張床造短左，床尾用黎放喼同埋鞋盒。自己再喺房痴啲牆貼同poster，間房就靚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲細位可以之後再慢慢諗點執，我之後都diy左唔少野，例如喺床尾位吉位整左塊摺板擺野，喺書枱底上兩口釘掛住個垃圾筒，買左個架喺書枱底放音箱等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58c1d337dbf51da12d6503e7cbc47e3646b8ff4","tid":233693,"uid":48156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2HvUM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2HvUM6.jpg&h=b2af6bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36AQZC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36AQZC5.jpg&h=b3676a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umF6RM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumF6RM4.jpg&h=fe97af3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a3afeb32b514a6bc8926b3e75ec4d597b0b5f5","tid":233693,"uid":37021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2HvUM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2HvUM6.jpg&h=b2af6bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36AQZC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36AQZC5.jpg&h=b3676a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umF6RM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumF6RM4.jpg&h=fe97af3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前住雜物房嗰陣都係類似咁擺<br />\n不過係碌架床下面係衣櫃<br />\n再連住張枱喺有窗口幅牆度<br />\n咁樣住落<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似</span>冇咁逼</blockquote><br />\n仲諗緊我有覆過post咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42449a246d7b03243518000585e95349c6320246","tid":233693,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2HvUM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2HvUM6.jpg&h=b2af6bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36AQZC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36AQZC5.jpg&h=b3676a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umF6RM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumF6RM4.jpg&h=fe97af3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前住雜物房嗰陣都係類似咁擺<br />\n不過係碌架床下面係衣櫃<br />\n再連住張枱喺有窗口幅牆度<br />\n咁樣住落<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似</span>冇咁逼</blockquote><br />\n仲諗緊我有覆過post咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇左幾次先搵到有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608df83c96fa8b0e2d64094cd2300b9eb8e4ce90","tid":233693,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ab68050ff50618477f2282a8456e66f5f26a99","tid":233693,"uid":50442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"同你間房差不多大但有尺半比咗個窗台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係同上面張圖一樣咁擺"},{"pid":"e6421e9cfdbf9ed9e1e6142f2b1334716b6d6f73","tid":233693,"uid":40228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"之前間房同上面張圖差唔多<br />\n不過會唔夠陽光，同埋訓上面無咁方便"},{"pid":"1903a57ac21d21d5a041d3abcda93874d0df3b6e","tid":233693,"uid":92340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"樓主自己個諗法就OK, 空間有限就要學識「斷捨離」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52g3i8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52g3i8t.jpg&h=60adbce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43qKg6y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43qKg6y.jpg&h=cafe814c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MN2xS8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMN2xS8w.jpg&h=393a724c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2z1780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2z1780.jpg&h=fde950c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f94da95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff94da95.jpg&h=27f53b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好就行超簡約主義，冷氣都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seBL26Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F